        <li>² If a model has at least one melee weapon AND one pistol, gains +1 Attack in melee.</li>
        <li>³ A model can fire up to two pistols, OR other eligible weapons (not both).</li>
        <li>⁴ Doubles shots at half range. With S&amp;S order only: can fire at full range too.</li>
