            <li>Uses own mini-AOP: 0–1 HQ · 1–2 Troops · 0–1 Elite/FA/HS per Troop · 0–ᵀ Transports.</li>
            <li>Cannot select a second AOP after filling all slots.</li>
            <li>May select own Army Customisation options.</li>
          </ul>
